ernment dangerous three i think coercive taxation is theft and government has a moral duty to keep it to a minimum william weld government think moral i extend that to the abortion issue i extend that to the socalled gay rights issue i think this is a freedom principle and consistent with the analysis in the economic area as well william weld freedom gay think do we believe that there is equal economic opportunity out there in the real world right now for each and every one of these groups if we believed in the tooth fairy if we believed in the easter bunny we might well believe that william weld opportunity world believe people arent stupid i mean people remember in  the unemployment rate was  percent now its   percent weve got  million jobs that weve created william weld stupid remember people natural resources are so vast that no single individual or business is going to protect them they dont have an incentive to william weld business single protect much is forgiven anyone who relieves the desperate boredom of the working press william weld working boredom press i have come to realize that jesse helms stands for everything in politics that is anathema to me william weld politics realize me i dare say that a majority of the american people think that having a fair hearing on an issue of importance in our relations with mexico is extremely important to our national interest as well as theirs william weld american people important if we have major geographic areas within our continent that have a tremendous lack of economic opportunity we found that that is going to produce instability  economic political and social william weld opportunity political liberals often dont see the problems and conservatives dont see the promise of government william weld government problems see so government acts as a safeguard of our property william weld government property our government has a role as well in what is referred to as redistributive justice william weld justice government well the system that had grown up in most states is that wealthy districts with an affluent population can afford to spend a lot more on their public school systems than the poorer districts william weld school population more one of the functions of government is to act as a safeguard not just of property but of our liberties william weld government property act government is never so noble as when it is addressing wrongs william weld government noble never in the nineteenth century slavery was the greatest wrong and government never stood so tall as when it was redressing that wrong william weld greatest government wrong i think government has a major role to play in helping us with the pursuit of happiness william weld happiness government play there are several such issues where i have departed radically from the republican orthodoxy william weld republican issues departed we absolutely have to restrain concentrations of wealth in industry from spoiling the situation for everybody william weld wealth situation industry its healthy for government to be a kind of moral catalyst using the bully pulpit of high office william weld government healthy moral government can contribute to a shared sense of purpose on the part of the citizenry thats its highest and best application william weld best purpose government before my tenure people didnt seem to think that citizens had a right to limit the size of their government william weld government people limit my slogan when i ran was that there is no such thing as government money there is only taxpayers money and that cut pretty deep william weld money deep government i dont understand the democrats approach to social security in this country and im not alone william weld alone security country micro managing anything is not a great role for government william weld great government role share this page cite this page citation find on amazon william weld related authors benjamin franklin alexander hamilton robert ken